  "description": "This intracranial electroencephalography (iEEG) dataset investigates neural spatial volatility in patients undergoing clinical evaluation. This dataset is a NEMAR mirror of the OpenNeuro ds006107 dataset. The dataset contains raw iEEG recordings collected from multiple subjects and is intended to support research on spatiotemporal dynamics of neural activity and clinical applications in epilepsy monitoring and localization.",
